## Online vs Offline Serving

| Aspect | Offline (Batch) | Online (Real-time) |
|--------|-----------------|-------------------|
| Latency | Minutes to hours | < 10ms |
| Freshness | Hours to days | Seconds to minutes |
| Use case | Training, batch inference | Real-time inference |
| Storage | Data warehouse, Parquet | Redis, DynamoDB |
| Compute | Spark, Dask | Pre-computed, streaming |

### Parity Between Online and Offline

- [ ] Same feature computation logic used for both online and offline
- [ ] Feature values are compared between online and offline regularly
- [ ] Any discrepancy triggers an alert and investigation
- [ ] Feature transformations are versioned alongside model versions

